Description: PYPI Server
        ===========
        
        .. image:: https://travis-ci.org/mosquito/pypi-server.svg?branch=master
            :target: https://travis-ci.org/mosquito/pypi-server
        
        .. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/pypi-server.svg
